WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.670
Good evening, everybody. Or good

00:00:03.680 --> 00:00:06.030
morning or good evening family,

00:00:06.040 --> 00:00:07.790
wherever you

00:00:07.790 --> 00:00:07.800
are.

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.310
I'm thankful for every single one of you

00:00:09.320 --> 00:00:12.350
being here with us. Last night was

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:15.590
different.

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:20.470
I didn't feel

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:22.910
like we quite pushed over what we needed

00:00:22.920 --> 00:00:25.230
to in the time frame we had. I told Diana after it was over

00:00:25.230 --> 00:00:25.240
that

00:00:25.240 --> 00:00:27.590
I felt like we were just right

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:29.590
there and we didn't get there. I was

00:00:29.600 --> 00:00:32.230
kind of annoyed with it,

00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:35.430
trying to do this in

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:37.470
a matter of just two hours. I'll try to

00:00:37.480 --> 00:00:40.270
talk less tonight and pray more.

00:00:40.280 --> 00:00:41.790
We're so thankful for every single

00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:43.830
one of you, and thank you for being here.

00:00:43.840 --> 00:00:46.190
I want to go over some of the things

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:48.510
the Lord showed us last night. Braden

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:50.350
has some things for you all that he

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:52.790
worked hard on today

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:55.230
to show you what's going on in

00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:58.350
the news related to what we prayed over.

00:00:58.360 --> 00:01:01.430
One of the things I think is really neat

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:02.670
is

00:01:02.680 --> 00:01:06.030
the Lord showed us about praying over

00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:08.870
schools and mass shootings.

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:10.950
Yesterday,

00:01:10.960 --> 00:01:14.910
a video showed a hero

00:01:14.920 --> 00:01:18.510
Oklahoma school principal tackle a gunman

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:21.910
who was allegedly inspired by the Columbine

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:25.110
massacre. Can we show the

00:01:25.120 --> 00:01:26.990
clip?

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:35.430
The principal took him

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:38.030
down immediately. He was shot in

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:40.350
the leg, but

00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:42.830
watch how fast he moves.

00:01:42.830 --> 00:01:42.840
The

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:44.790
principal

00:01:44.790 --> 00:01:44.800
is

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:46.510
on

00:01:46.520 --> 00:01:48.510
him.

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:51.670
I believe that's a result of prayer.

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:53.470
The young man was

00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:56.430
deranged and said he was

00:01:56.440 --> 00:01:58.310
inspired by Columbine. He

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:00.110
had over 100 rounds

00:02:00.110 --> 00:02:00.120
and

00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:02.870
was going to go in and

00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:04.630
do whatever he thought he was going

00:02:04.640 --> 00:02:07.670
to do. Prayer changes things.

00:02:07.670 --> 00:02:07.680
I

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:09.270
want to give all the glory to God

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:10.389
because this was

00:02:10.399 --> 00:02:13.630
Oklahoma and that principal was a hero.

00:02:13.640 --> 00:02:16.350
He took that young man out.

00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:18.390
The

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:21.670
principal was shot, but

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:23.750
thank God they kicked the gun

00:02:23.760 --> 00:02:26.710
away.

00:02:26.720 --> 00:02:28.990
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:30.550
I don't know why that principal was on

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:32.949
alert like that so quickly, but isn't

00:02:32.959 --> 00:02:35.030
Jesus wonderful that

00:02:35.030 --> 00:02:35.040
this

00:02:35.040 --> 00:02:36.670
happened

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:39.430
yesterday?

00:02:42.440 --> 00:02:44.190
I believe that is a result of

00:02:44.200 --> 00:02:46.430
prayer. He said he was going to try to

00:02:46.440 --> 00:02:49.990
do something like Columbine.

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:54.870
It's time to give God praise whenever we

00:02:54.880 --> 00:02:56.790
see something like that happen.

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:58.470
That principal was ready to

00:02:58.470 --> 00:02:58.480
tackle that kid

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:00.790
in seconds.

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:08.870
How did he know? I would say by the

00:03:08.880 --> 00:03:10.949
leading of the Holy Spirit.

00:03:10.959 --> 00:03:14.030
A

00:03:14.040 --> 00:03:15.390
