00:03:15.400 --> 00:03:17.670
state of Oklahoma in Purcell, I believe,

00:03:17.670 --> 00:03:17.680
or

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:19.390
Pauls Valley.

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:26.750
It's down closer to Ardmore, closer to Texas,

00:03:26.760 --> 00:03:28.350
but

00:03:28.350 --> 00:03:28.360
it's

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:30.790
pretty amazing what the Lord did there.

